<form action="register" class="form-inline">
	<b>Isn't your hub shown?</b><br />
	<small>If your hub has been down for too many days our spider 
	probably marked it as <i>dead</i>. So add it here again!<br />
	<input type="text" class="form-control" style="max-width:30em"
			name="baseUrl" value="https://" maxlength="128"
			placeholder="Enter base URL of your hub">
	<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Add it!</button>
	</small>
</form>